  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature critically fails on a melee Strike's attack roll against you.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The triggering creature is within your reach, you have at least one free active hand, and your target is no more than one size larger than you.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You seize the opportunity to give your foe a big hug to help them feel better or calm down. You attempt an Athletics check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.PMbdMWc2QroouFGD]{Grapple} the triggering creature.</p>"
